'''2016年菲律賓總統、副總統選舉'''於2016年5月9日舉行。根據[[菲律賓憲法|1987年菲律賓憲法]]，时任總統[[阿基諾三世|阿基諾三世]]任期屆滿六年無法連任。由於第十六任總統和副總統為分別選出，故總統和副總統當選人可能來自不同政黨，其競選搭檔也是不同人。

該次選舉是自{{le|1935年菲律賓總統選舉|Philippine presidential election, 1935}}以來菲律賓第16場總統選舉，亦是自1986年以來菲律賓第6場總統選舉。{{le|2016年菲律賓總統選舉|2016 Philippine Presidential Election}}同時進行，選出包括[[棉蘭老穆斯林自治區|棉蘭老穆斯林自治區]]在內的[[巴朗圭|巴朗圭]]級以上的參眾議院和政府。

5月9日選舉結果，菲律賓民主黨–人民力量所屬的候選人[[罗德里戈·杜特地|罗德里戈·杜特地]]獲得16,601,997票，得票率39.01%，擊敗對手{{le|馬爾·羅哈斯|Mar Roxas}}、[[格蕾丝·波因|格蕾丝·波因]]等人，當選總統。

副總統選舉則由馬爾·羅哈斯的搭檔、[[菲律賓自由黨|自由黨]]眾議員[[萊妮·羅布雷多|萊妮·羅布雷多]]以14,418,817票、35.11%得票率險勝對手[[小费迪南德·马科斯|小费迪南德·马科斯]]，當選菲律賓副總統。

下次選舉為[[2022年菲律賓總統選舉|2022年菲律賓總統選舉]]

==選舉制度==
自1992年起，菲律賓總統選舉每隔六年在五月的第二個星期一舉行。時任總統阿基諾三世在是屆選舉中不能再尋求連任，但時任副總統[[傑約馬爾·比奈|傑約馬爾·比奈]]仍可尋求連任。例外的是曾在1998年當選總統的[[約瑟夫·埃斯特拉達|約瑟夫·埃斯特拉達]]，因離任時並未完成一半的總統任期，故被允許參加[[2010年菲律賓總統選舉|2010年總統選舉]]。

菲律賓總統以[[簡單多數制|簡單多數制]]選出：票數最多的候選人即使未達絕對多數仍成為候任菲律賓總統。副總統則分開選舉，但以同樣方式選出，選民亦可將總統票和副總統票投給不同政黨的候選人。當選總統和副總統會在2016年6月30日起中午起開始其六年任期，直至2022年6月30日為止。

候選人是透過不同政黨的政治会议推舉的。菲律賓大部份政黨的組織均較為鬆散，政治人物經常易黨參選，故不獲政黨提名的候選人可能會以獨立候選人、另一政黨或自組政黨身份參選。候選人的推舉程序受[[菲律賓選舉委員會|菲律賓選舉委員會]]的監察，該委員會亦負責規範及舉辦選舉。委員會取消「具擾亂性的」候選人或無法凝聚全國選民的候選人資格的情況並不罕見。此導致了候選人的人數受到限制。總統選舉的選舉活動歷時3個月，自2016年2月初開始至選舉日前夕為止，[[濯足節|濯足節]]和[[耶穌受難日|耶穌受難日]]時暫停選舉活動。

點票工作先在個別選區進行，然後再進依次序行市內及省內點票，而[[菲律賓國會|菲律賓國會]]是最後的點票機關。而選後對結果的異議則由[[菲律賓最高法院|菲律賓最高法院]]的[[总统选举法庭|总统选举法庭]]負責處理。

==背景==
[[File:2010PhilippineVicePresidentialElection.png|thumb]]勝出的省份及城市以藍色標示。]]
時任[[菲律賓自由黨|菲律賓自由黨]]參議員貝尼格諾·阿基諾三世在2010年總統選舉中贏得42.08%的選票，擊敗曾在2001年因貪污罪名而下台的前總統約瑟夫·埃斯特拉達和其他候選人。與此同時，埃斯特拉達的競選搭檔，來自[[菲律賓民主黨–人民力量|菲律賓民主黨–人民力量]]的時任[[马卡蒂|马卡蒂]]市長傑約馬爾·比奈在同年的副總統選舉中擊敗阿基諾三世的競選搭檔，來自自由黨的[[馬爾·羅哈斯|馬爾·羅哈斯]]和其他候選人<ref name="June 9">{{cite news|url = http://www.gmanews.tv/story/193035/congress-proclaims-aquino-as-president-binay-as-vp|title = Congress proclaims Aquino as president, Binay as VP|first = JAM|last = SISANTE|work = GMAnews.tv|accessdate = 2010-06-09|archive-date = 2010-06-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100609083601/http://www.gmanews.tv/story/193035/congress-proclaims-aquino-as-president-binay-as-vp|dead-url = no}}</ref>。羅哈斯在總統選舉法庭中指控比奈賄選，要求判決一部份投給比奈的票無效<ref name="Bordadora2">{{cite web|title = ‘Automated mystery’ case: Roxas files protest|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/inquirerheadlines/nation/view/20100710-280198/Automated-mystery-case-Roxas-files-protest|publisher = Philippine Daily Inquirer|last = Bordadora|first = Norman|date = 2010-07-10|accessdate = 2010-07-11|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100711070951/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/inquirerheadlines/nation/view/20100710-280198/Automated-mystery-case-Roxas-files-protest|archivedate = 2010-07-11}}</ref>。

比奈和羅哈斯後來都被阿基諾三世任命為內閣成員。比奈領導房屋及市區發展協調委員會<ref>{{Cite web|title = Binay joins Cabinet as housing czar - INQUIRER.net, Philippine News for Filipinos|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/inquirerheadlines/nation/view/20100716-281408/Binay-joins-Cabinet-as-housing-czar|website = Philippine Daily Inquirer|accessdate = 2015-05-31|date = 2010-07-26|last = Burgonio|first = TJ|last2 = Balana|first2 = Cynthia|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150619180331/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/inquirerheadlines/nation/view/20100716-281408/Binay-joins-Cabinet-as-housing-czar|archivedate = 2015-06-19}}</ref>，而羅哈斯首先在2011年獲阿基諾三世委任為[[菲律賓交通及通訊部|交通及通訊部]]部長，其後獲委任為[[菲律賓內政及地方政府部|內政及地方政府部]]部長<ref>{{Cite web|title = Roxas takes oath as DILG secretary|url = http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/276121/news/nation/roxas-takes-oath-as-dilg-secretary|accessdate = 2015-05-31|date = 2012-09-29|website = GMA News Online|first = |last = |archive-date = 2015-06-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150619174319/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/276121/news/nation/roxas-takes-oath-as-dilg-secretary|dead-url = no}}</ref>。截至2014年，由於自由黨和民主黨間的初步協议和比奈的反控，有關比奈賄選的審訊仍未進行<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2014/08/08/1355168/roxas-poll-protest-vs-binay-still-preliminary-stage|title = Roxas poll protest vs Binay still in preliminary stage|last = Punay|first = Edu|date = 2014-08-14|work = The Philippine Star|access-date = 2015-06-01|via = |archive-date = 2014-08-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140808071005/http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2014/08/08/1355168/roxas-poll-protest-vs-binay-still-preliminary-stage|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

在[[2013年菲律賓參議院選舉|2013年參議院選舉]]中，阿基諾三世和羅哈斯組成[[普諾伊團隊|普諾伊團隊]]<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.philstar.com/Article.aspx?articleId=824160&publicationSubCategoryId=63|title = LP, NP, NPC eye common ticket|first = Jess|last = Diaz|work = Philippine Star|date = 2012-07-05|accessdate = 2012-07-05}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。而埃斯特拉達和比奈則組成[[聯合民族主義聯盟|聯合民族主義聯盟]]<ref>{{cite news|url = http://ph.news.yahoo.com/uno-una-erap-binay-unite-160000213.html|title = From UNO to UNA, Erap, Binay unite|first = Marvin|last = Sy|work = Philippine Star|publisher = Yahoo! Philippines News|date = 2012-04-04|accessdate = 2012-04-05|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120406121327/http://ph.news.yahoo.com/uno-una-erap-binay-unite-160000213.html|archivedate = 2012-04-06}}</ref>。 普諾伊團隊在該次選舉中贏得9個議席，而聯合民族主義聯盟只取得3個議席<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2013/05/19/943716/final-3-senators-elect-proclaimed|title = Final 3 senators-elect proclaimed|first = Shiela|last = Crisostomo|work = Philippine Star|date = 2013-05-19|accessdate = 2013-05-19|archive-date = 2013-06-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130608075153/http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2013/05/19/943716/final-3-senators-elect-proclaimed|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2014年3月，民主黨退出聯合民族主義聯盟。在此前一週，比奈因「領袖間的分歧」辭任聯合民族主義聯盟主席。在2013年參議院選舉時，聯合民族主義聯盟總裁[[阿基林奧·皮門特爾三世|阿基林奧·皮門特爾三世]]和比奈就是否將在[[2007年菲律賓參議院選舉|2007年參議院選舉]]中被指控舞弊的[[胡安·米格爾·蘇比里|胡安·米格爾·蘇比里]]列入聯合民族主義聯盟的候選人名單公開爭辯<ref>{{Cite web|title = PDP-Laban bolts UNA after Binay resigns as chairman|url = http://www.interaksyon.com/article/82193/pdp-laban-bolts-una-after-binay-resigns-as-chairman|accessdate = 2015-05-31|date = 2014-03-07|website = Interaksyon.com|last = Reyes|first = Ernie|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924044849/http://www.interaksyon.com/article/82193/pdp-laban-bolts-una-after-binay-resigns-as-chairman|archivedate = 2015-09-24}}</ref>。

一些聯合民族主義聯盟的中堅份子，如曾意圖成為比奈競選搭檔的參議員[[胡安·蓬塞·恩里萊|胡安·蓬塞·恩里萊]]和[[興戈伊·埃斯特拉達|興戈伊·埃斯特拉達]]，以及考慮參選總統的[[基督教穆斯林民主力量黨|基督教穆斯林民主力量黨]]參議員[[邦·雷維利亞|邦·雷維利亞]]因[[優先發展援助基金詐騙案|優先發展援助基金詐騙案]]而被扣押<ref>{{Cite web|title = Jinggoy Estrada ordered arrested by Sandiganbayan|url = http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/366886/news/nation/jinggoy-estrada-ordered-arrested-by-sandiganbayan|accessdate = May 31, 2015|date = 2014-06-23|website = GMA News Online|last = Chiu|first = Patricia Denise|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304043218/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/366886/news/nation/jinggoy-estrada-ordered-arrested-by-sandiganbayan|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Sen. Bong Revilla surrenders to Sandiganbayan, files motion for bail|url = http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/366541/news/nation/sen-bong-revilla-surrenders-to-sandiganbayan-files-motion-for-bail|accessdate = 2015-05-31|date = 2014-06-20|website = GMA News Online|last = Legaspi|first = Amita|archive-date = 2015-07-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150716092126/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/366541/news/nation/sen-bong-revilla-surrenders-to-sandiganbayan-files-motion-for-bail|dead-url = no}}</ref>。沒有自由黨人在這宗案件中受到牽連。這些政府認為是反貪腐舉動的行動被聯合民族主義聯盟認為是政治檢控<ref>{{Cite web|title = Binay hits Aquino admin|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/646918/binay-hits-aquino-admin|website = Philippine Daily Inquirer|accessdate = 2015-05-31|first = Niña|last = Calleja|archive-date = 2015-06-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150625084640/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/646918/binay-hits-aquino-admin|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2014年7月，2013年馬卡蒂市長選舉落選人雷納托·邦達爾向[[菲律賓監察專員公署|菲律賓監察專員公署]]指控時任馬卡蒂市長[[小赫霍馬爾·比奈|小赫霍馬爾·比奈]]和他身為副總統的父親貪污。一個月後，[[菲律賓參議院藍絲帶委員會|菲律賓參議院藍絲帶委員會]]成立一個由皮門特爾和[[菲律賓國民黨|菲律賓國民黨]]成員[[艾倫·彼得·卡耶坦奧|艾倫·彼得·卡耶坦奧]]和[[安东尼奥·特里兰尼斯|安东尼奥·特里兰尼斯]]組成的委員會，開始就比奈出任馬卡蒂市長期間被控因馬卡蒂市政廳新翼超支問題而衍生的貪污案展開聆訊<ref>{{Cite web|title = Binay accusers in Makati building case file new petition; Nancy says she won't use proxies|url = http://www.interaksyon.com/article/93527/binay-accusers-in-makati-building-case-file-new-petition-nancy-says-she-wont-use-proxies|accessdate = 2015-05-31|date = 2014-08-18|website = Interkasyon.com|last = |first = |deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140823003412/http://www.interaksyon.com/article/93527/binay-accusers-in-makati-building-case-file-new-petition-nancy-says-she-wont-use-proxies|archivedate = 2014-08-23}}</ref>。


比奈否認指控<ref>{{Cite web|title = Binay: All recycled lies|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/639064/binay-all-recycled-lies|website = Philippine Daily Inquirer|accessdate = 2015-05-31|first = Christine|last = Avendaño|date = 2015-09-19|archive-date = 2015-06-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150628144442/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/639064/binay-all-recycled-lies|dead-url = no}}</ref>，但他並沒出席參議院的聆訊<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.rappler.com/nation/72683-jejomar-binay-senate-investigation-makati|title = VP Binay still a no-show as Senate hearings resume|last = Cupin|first = Bea|date = 2014-10-22|work = Rappler.com|access-date = 2015-06-01|via = |archive-date = 2014-12-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141223014844/http://www.rappler.com/nation/72683-jejomar-binay-senate-investigation-makati|dead-url = no}}</ref>。聯合民族主義聯盟秘書長J·V·包蒂斯塔認為調查旨在阻止比奈出任總統的計劃，而羅哈斯、卡耶坦奧和特里兰尼斯則在背後策動這個計劃。他亦指控商人薩爾瓦多·薩莫拉出資支持這個計劃<ref>{{Cite web|title = ‘Oplan Nognog: LP plot vs Binay’ - Manila Standard Today|url = http://manilastandardtoday.com/2014/10/14/-oplan-nognog-lp-plot-vs-binay-/|accessdate = 2015-06-19|website = The New Standard|publisher = |date = 2014-10-14|last = Herrera|first = Christine F.|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141220075110/http://manilastandardtoday.com/2014/10/14/-oplan-nognog-lp-plot-vs-binay-|archive-date = 2014-12-20|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。2015年5月，[[菲律賓上訴法院|菲律賓上訴法院]]在[[菲律賓反洗錢委員會|菲律賓反洗錢委員會]]和菲律賓監察專員公署的請求下，頒令凍結比奈242個銀行戶口六個月。比奈陣營認為，此事是自由黨在背後策動<ref>{{Cite web|title = CA freezes Binay’s bank accounts - The Manila Times Online|url = http://www.manilatimes.net/ca-freezes-binays-bank-accounts/183128/|accessdate = 2015-06-07|date = 2015-05-13|website = The Manila Times|publisher = |last = Canlas|first = Jomar|archive-date = 2015-06-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150615042929/http://www.manilatimes.net/ca-freezes-binays-bank-accounts/183128/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。但被屬自由黨的總統阿基諾否認<ref>{{Cite web|title = PNoy denies LP hand in freezing of VP Binay’s bank accounts|url = http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/487058/news/nation/pnoy-denies-lp-hand-in-freezing-of-vp-binay-s-bank-accounts|accessdate = 2015-06-07|date = 2015-05-14|website = GMA News Online|last = Calonzo|first = Andreo|archive-date = 2015-06-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150616002853/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/487058/news/nation/pnoy-denies-lp-hand-in-freezing-of-vp-binay-s-bank-accounts|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2015年5月下旬，委員會發表報告，提議將比奈的貪污案交到參議院討論，該報告由委員會的三名成員和[[格蕾丝·波因|格蕾丝·波因]]聯署<ref>{{Cite web|title = Grace Poe signs report recommending plunder raps vs. VP Binay|url = http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/495058/news/nation/grace-poe-signs-report-recommending-plunder-raps-vs-vp-binay|accessdate = 2015-06-13|date = 2015-05-29|website = GMA News Online|last = Sisante|first = Jam|archive-date = 2015-05-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150530004926/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/495058/news/nation/grace-poe-signs-report-recommending-plunder-raps-vs-vp-binay|dead-url = no}}</ref>。至同年6月上旬，已有10名參議員聯署報告，使報告正式生效<ref>{{Cite web|title = 10 senators sign subcommittee report vs Binay|url = http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2015/06/02/1461329/10-senators-sign-subcommittee-report-vs-binay|accessdate = 2015-06-13|date = 2015-06-02|website = The Philippine Star|last = Sy|first = Marvin|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150615235723/http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2015/06/02/1461329/10-senators-sign-subcommittee-report-vs-binay|archivedate = 2015-06-15|df = }}</ref>。一個月後，比奈在馬卡蒂地方裁判法院指控卡耶坦奧、特里兰尼斯和其他人「精心組織和策劃」對他的誹謗和阻止他就任總統，要求索償2億[[菲律賓披索|菲律賓披索]]<ref>{{Cite web|title = VIDEO {{!}} VP Binay files P200-M damage suit over 'orchestrated' smear drive to derail 2016 candidacy|url = http://www.interaksyon.com/article/114508/vp-binay-files-p200-m-damage-suit-over-orchestrated-smear-drive-to-derail-2016-candidacy|accessdate = 2015-07-22|date = 2015-07-20|website = Interaksyon.com|authorlink = |last2 = Francisco|first2 = Jove|first = Ernie|last = Reyes|publisher = News5|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150721074705/http://www.interaksyon.com/article/114508/vp-binay-files-p200-m-damage-suit-over-orchestrated-smear-drive-to-derail-2016-candidacy|archivedate = 2015-07-21}}</ref>。 

與此同時，阿基諾與羅哈斯、波因和[[弗朗西斯·埃斯庫德羅|弗朗西斯·埃斯庫德羅]]會面，決定自由黨競逐總統的人選。儘管當時沒有人宣佈其參選意向，阿基諾需要在2015年7月發佈其任內最後一份国情咨文時決定支持的人選。參眾兩院議長富蘭克林·德里隆和小費利西阿諾·貝爾蒙特否認自由黨黨員不滿意阿基诺的优柔寡断，並表示自由黨仍然團結<ref>{{Cite web|title = LP united; 2016 talks on schedule — Belmonte, Drilon|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/706668/lp-united-2016-talks-on-schedule-belmonte-drilon|website = INQUIRER.net|accessdate = 2015-07-22|first = Kristine Angeli|last = Sabillo|date = 2015-07-21|archive-date = 2015-07-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150722043923/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/706668/lp-united-2016-talks-on-schedule-belmonte-drilon|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2015年7月上旬，聯合民族主義聯盟正式以政黨名義成立，由比奈出任主席<ref name=":22">{{Cite web|title = Main opposition party UNA launched|url = http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2015/07/02/1472361/main-opposition-party-una-launched|accessdate = 2015-07-02|date = 2015-07-02|publisher = The Philippine Star|first = Helen|last = Flores|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150702200529/http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2015/07/02/1472361/main-opposition-party-una-launched|archivedate = 2015-07-02|df = }}</ref>。其後，阿基諾亦決定推舉羅哈斯參選總統，並獲後者接受<ref name=":4" />。同年8月，[[達沃市|達沃市]]市長[[罗德里戈·杜特地|罗德里戈·杜特地]]決定在市長任期完結後退休，但網上有強烈聲音請求他參選<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.rappler.com/nation/politics/elections/2016/105037-duterte-not-running|title = Duterte: 'I am not running for president'|publisher = Rappler|accessdate = 2015-09-08|archive-date = 2015-09-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150908024858/http://www.rappler.com/nation/politics/elections/2016/105037-duterte-not-running|dead-url = no}}</ref>。波因在同年9月中旬宣佈競逐總統職位<ref>{{Cite web|title = Poe in 2016 {{!}} mb.com.ph {{!}} Philippine News|url = http://www.mb.com.ph/poe-in-2016/|website = Manila Bulletin|accessdate = 2015-09-17|first = Hannah|last = Torregoza|date = 2015-09-16|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150920000423/http://www.mb.com.ph/poe-in-2016/|archivedate = 2015-09-20}}</ref>，而埃斯庫德羅亦在波因宣佈參選總統的翌日宣佈成為波因的競選搭檔<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|title = It’s official: Grace Poe, Chiz Escudero to run together in 2016|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/722778/its-official-grace-poe-chiz-escudero-to-run-together-in-2016|first = Maila|last = Ager|accessdate = September 21, 2015|website = INQUIRER.net|date = September 17, 2015|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045830/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/722778/its-official-grace-poe-chiz-escudero-to-run-together-in-2016|dead-url = no}}</ref>。幾天後，卡耶坦奧參選副總統，並表示想成為杜特地的競選搭檔。

2015年10月3日，特里兰尼斯宣佈以獨立候選人身份參選副總統，並在總統選舉中支持波因<ref>{{Cite web|title = Trillanes running for VP, Magdalo group backs Poe|url = http://www.rappler.com/nation/politics/elections/2016/107972-trillanes-running-for-vp-magdalo-group-backs-poe|website = Rappler|publisher = |accessdate = 2015-10-27|date = 2015-10-03|archive-date = 2015-10-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151008084258/http://www.rappler.com/nation/politics/elections/2016/107972-trillanes-running-for-vp-magdalo-group-backs-poe|dead-url = no}}</ref>。幾天後，眾議員[[萊妮·羅布雷多|萊妮·羅布雷多]]成為羅哈斯的競選搭檔<ref name=":6">{{cite news|last1=Cruz|first1=RG|title=Leni is Mar's running mate|url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/10/05/15/leni-mars-running-mate|accessdate=2015-10-06|work=ABS-CBN News and Current Affairs|publisher=ABS-CBN Corporation|date=2015-10-05|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007020353/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/10/05/15/leni-mars-running-mate|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在羅布雷多宣佈參選的同一天，參議員[[小费迪南德·马科斯|小费迪南德·马科斯]]亦宣佈參選副總統<ref name=":7">{{Cite news|url = http://cnnphilippines.com/news/2015/10/05/bongbong-marcos-vice-president-elections-2016-the-filipino-votes.html|title = Bongbong Marcos running for vice president in 2016|last = |first = |date = 2015-10-05|work = CNN Philippines|access-date = 2015-10-05|via = |archive-date = 2015-10-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151008085446/http://cnnphilippines.com/news/2015/10/05/bongbong-marcos-vice-president-elections-2016-the-filipino-votes.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。一星期後，參議員[[格雷戈里奧·霍納桑|格雷戈里奧·霍納桑]]獲聯合民族主義聯盟提名競逐副總統，並成為比奈的競選搭檔<ref name=":8">{{cite web|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/718076/now-its-honasan-as-possible-binay-running-mate|title=Now it’s Honasan as possible Binay running mate|author=Delfin T. Mallari Jr.|publisher=|accessdate=2016-04-15|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114101/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/718076/now-its-honasan-as-possible-binay-running-mate|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同一天，參議員[[米麗阿姆·德芬索爾·聖地牙哥|米麗阿姆·德芬索爾·聖地牙哥]]宣佈參選總統<ref name=":9">{{cite web|title = Miriam announces presidential run in 2016|url = http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/540496/news/nation/miriam-announces-presidential-run-in-2016|website = GMA News|first = Jessica|last = Bartolome|accessdate = 2015-10-13|date = 2015-10-13|archive-date = 2015-11-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151123010926/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/540496/news/nation/miriam-announces-presidential-run-in-2016|dead-url = no}}</ref>。幾天後，她宣佈小费迪南德·马科斯成為她的競選搭檔<ref name=":10">{{Cite web|title = Miriam Santiago confirms Bongbong Marcos is her vice president|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/731184/miriam-santiago-confirms-bongbong-marcos-is-her-veep|website = INQUIRER.net|accessdate = 2015-10-27|date = 2015-10-15|last = Hegina|first = Aries Joseph|archive-date = 2015-10-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151017210325/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/731184/miriam-santiago-confirms-bongbong-marcos-is-her-veep|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

在提名期最後一天，杜特地並沒有現身。民主黨派出[[馬丁·迪尼奧|馬丁·迪尼奧]]出選總統<ref name=":11">{{cite web|title = VACC chair Martin Diño files COC for president|url = http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/540938/news/nation/vacc-chair-martin-dino-files-coc-for-president|website = GMA News|accessdate = 2015-10-16|date = 2015-10-26|archive-date = 2015-11-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151125025124/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/540938/news/nation/vacc-chair-martin-dino-files-coc-for-president|dead-url = no}}</ref>。同一天，有超過100人參選總統。 

