====米麗阿姆·德芬索爾·聖地牙哥====
2014年7月2日，參議員米麗阿姆·德芬索爾·聖地牙哥宣佈她罹患第四期[[肺癌|肺癌]]，並表示如果病情得到缓解就會第三度參選總統。聖地牙哥曾在1992年參選總統，後來在1995年晉身參議院。她曾在1998年再度參選總統<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/368296/news/nation/senator-miriam-santiago-may-go-for-2016-presidential-bid-if |title=Senator Miriam Santiago may go for 2016 presidential bid if... |work=GMA News |date=2014-07-02 |accessdate=2015-04-26 |archive-date=2015-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416145131/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/368296/news/nation/senator-miriam-santiago-may-go-for-2016-presidential-bid-if |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2014年11月，聖地牙哥在推特表示，如果2016年總統選舉時其病情有所進展，她就會參選總統。在給參議院的信中，聖地牙哥表示其體內超過九成的癌細胞已經清除<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/11/14/14/miriam-seriously-eyeing-presidency |title=Miriam seriously eyeing presidency |work=ABS-CBNnews.com |date=2014-11-15 |accessdate=2015-04-26 |archive-date=2015-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403004824/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/11/14/14/miriam-seriously-eyeing-presidency |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年10月13日，聖地牙哥在其新書發佈會中正式宣佈代表[[人民改革黨|人民改革黨]]參選總統<ref name=":9"/>。 幾天後，聖地牙哥表示參議員小费迪南德·马科斯會成為她的競選搭檔。她的政綱提倡引入國民認同的國際法、聚焦農業灌溉和建設农场到市场的道路以振興農業、在各省及各區設立至少一項政府工程以及根除贪污腐败。其中她認為贪污腐败是菲律賓貧困和低效率的原因<ref name=":10"/>。2015年11月，總統候選人罗德里戈·杜特地接受訪問，在提到其他總統候選人質素的時候表示：「如果你想要非凡的才干和忠诚，就投給米麗阿姆。」<ref name="no gasoline">{{cite news|title=Duterte has ‘car but no gasoline’ for 2016 race|url=http://www.bworldonline.com/content.php?id=119102|accessdate=11 February 2016|work=BusinessWorld Online|publisher=BusinessWorld Publishing Corporation|date=2015-11-23|archive-date=2019-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190110184435/http://www.bworldonline.com/content.php?id=119102|dead-url=no}}</ref>

====罗德里戈·杜特地====
早在2015年時，杜特地已暗示會參選2016年總統選舉，並承諾當選後會改革國會<ref>{{cite news |url=http://manila.coconuts.co/2015/01/26/duterte-talks-about-what-hell-do-if-hes-elected-president-2016 |title=Duterte talks about what he'll do if he's elected president in 2016 |newspaper=Coconuts Manila |date=2015-01-26 |accessdate=2016-04-15 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305181555/http://manila.coconuts.co/2015/01/26/duterte-talks-about-what-hell-do-if-hes-elected-president-2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://ph.news.yahoo.com/duterte-eyes-abolition-congress-000000572.html |title=Duterte eyes abolition of Congress |newspaper=Yahoo News Philippines |date=2015-01-26 |first=Ben |last=Serrano |accessdate=2016-04-15 |archive-date=2015-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205015122/https://ph.news.yahoo.com/duterte-eyes-abolition-congress-000000572.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.philstar.com/nation/2015/01/26/1416721/duterte-eyes-abolition-congress-if-elected-president-2016 |title=Duterte eyes abolition of Congress if elected president in 2016 |newspaper=The Philippine Star |first=Ben |last=Serrano |date=2015-01-26 |accessdate=2016-04-15 |archive-date=2016-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502210819/http://www.philstar.com/nation/2015/01/26/1416721/duterte-eyes-abolition-congress-if-elected-president-2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在此之前的2014年2月，杜特地已獲得一部份網民認同其在任達沃市市長時的表現，尤其認同他在維護達沃市安定和秩序上的表現。但他婉拒參選總統，並表示他不合資格擔綱更高級的職位<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mb.com.ph/duterte-shrugs-off-calls-to-run-for-president/|title=Duterte shrugs off calls to run for president|first=Mary Rose|last=Hogaza|work=Manila Bulletin|date=2014-02-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703112924/http://www.mb.com.ph/duterte-shrugs-off-calls-to-run-for-president/|archivedate=2015-07-03|accessdate=2016-04-15}}</ref>。一年後，杜特地在[[碧瑤市|碧瑤市]]表示他只會在拯救國家之時才會出選總統，他亦表示自己沒有競選總統所需的100至150億披索的競選經費<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.interaksyon.com/article/105388/duterte-to-run-for-president-if-only-to-save-the-republic-but-does-not-have-p10b-in-campaign-money |title=Duterte to run for president 'if only to save the republic' but does not have P10B in campaign money |first=Leonardo V. |last=Micua |work=Philippine News Agency |publisher=Interaksyon.com |date=2015-02-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221211132/http://www.interaksyon.com/article/105388/duterte-to-run-for-president-if-only-to-save-the-republic-but-does-not-have-p10b-in-campaign-money |archivedate=2015-02-21 |accessdate=2016-04-15 }}</ref>。但幾天後，杜特地重返民主黨。他表示他從沒退黨，只是在2013年選舉中以本地政黨名義參選，以提高勝算<ref>{{cite news|last1=Esmaquel|first1=Paterno II|title=Duterte 're-enters' PDP-Laban amid 2016 prospects|url=http://www.rappler.com/nation/84620-rodrigo-duterte-pdp-laban|accessdate=2015-06-01|work=Rappler.com|date=2015-02-21|archive-date=2015-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150601030730/http://www.rappler.com/nation/84620-rodrigo-duterte-pdp-laban|dead-url=no}}</ref>。民主黨總裁[[阿基林奧·皮門特爾三世|阿基林奧·皮門特爾三世]]其後表示杜特地是該黨2016年總統選舉的人選之一，因該黨[[聯邦主義|聯邦主義]]的立場與杜特地的主張不谋而合<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/441702/news/nation/pimentel-pdp-laban-might-field-davao-mayor-duterte-in-2016-polls |title=Pimentel: PDP-Laban might field Davao Mayor Duterte in 2016 polls |first=Amanda |last=Fernandez |work=GMA News Online |date=2015-02-21 |accessdate=2016-04-15 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304095014/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/441702/news/nation/pimentel-pdp-laban-might-field-davao-mayor-duterte-in-2016-polls |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在比奈打算邀請杜特地的消息傳出後幾天，杜特地發表聲明，表示沒興趣擔任國家級的職位<ref name="duterte may23">{{cite news |url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/05/23/15/duterte-i-wont-run-national-post-2016 |title=Duterte: I won't run for national post in 2016 |work=ABS-CBNnews.com |date=2015-05-23 |accessdate=2015-05-23 |archive-date=2015-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150525233752/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/05/23/15/duterte-i-wont-run-national-post-2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年9月，杜特地亦拒絕米麗阿姆·德芬索爾·聖地牙哥的邀請擔任其競選搭檔，並向聖地牙哥推薦前國務部長[[小希爾貝爾托·特奧多羅|小希爾貝爾托·特奧多羅]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/637306/poe-says-no-duterte-tells-santiago-take-gibo-teodoro |title=Poe says no; Duterte tells Santiago: Take Gibo Teodoro |work=INQUIRER.net |date=2014-09-14 |accessdate=2015-05-13 |archive-date=2014-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220094915/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/637306/poe-says-no-duterte-tells-santiago-take-gibo-teodoro |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但是，2015年10月，聖地亞哥決定其競選搭檔由小费迪南德·马科斯擔任<ref>{{cite web|title=Miriam Santiago: Bongbong Marcos is my running mate|url=http://www.rappler.com/nation/politics/elections/2016/109349-miriam-santiago-bongbong-marcos-is-my-running-mate|website=Rappler|accessdate=2016-04-15|archive-date=2016-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106151236/http://www.rappler.com/nation/politics/elections/2016/109349-miriam-santiago-bongbong-marcos-is-my-running-mate|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

其後，在他主持的電視節目中，杜特地表示他正尋求朋友和支持者的建議參選總統。他亦表示他開始不排除參選總統的可能性<ref>{{cite news|last1=Dioquino|first1=Rose-An Jessica|last2=Aguinaldo|first2=Sandra|title=Duterte says he will now ‘consider’ presidential bid|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/508242/news/nation/duterte-says-he-will-now-consider-presidential-bid|accessdate=2015-06-22|publisher=GMA News|date=2015-06-22|archive-date=2015-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622164821/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/508242/news/nation/duterte-says-he-will-now-consider-presidential-bid|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年9月7日，杜特地在達沃市召開記者會，宣佈不會參加2016年總統選舉，並向支持者致歉。他亦表示他會在其達沃市市長職務在2016年任滿時退出政壇，由其女兒[[莎拉·杜特地|莎拉·杜特地]]接棒。他亦表示因為年齡、健康和家庭原因而作出這個決定<ref>{{cite news|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/719960/dutertes-final-answer-i-wont-run-for-president|title=Duterte’s final answer: I won’t run for president|publisher=Inquirer.net|date=2015-09-07|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060403/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/719960/dutertes-final-answer-i-wont-run-for-president|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在他宣佈決定後，社交媒體反應不一，部份支持者繼續其請願，請求杜特地改變決定<ref>{{cite news|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/720327/dutertes-die-hard-fans-refuse-to-lose-hope-as-mayor-shows-up-in-events|title=Duterte’s die-hard fans refuse to lose hope as mayor shows up in events|publisher=Inquirer.net|date=2015-09-08|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100104/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/720327/dutertes-die-hard-fans-refuse-to-lose-hope-as-mayor-shows-up-in-events|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年9月26日，杜特地的支持者在馬尼拉[[黎剎公園|黎剎公園]]集會，請求杜特地參加2016年總統選舉<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.abs-cbn.com/nation/09/25/15/duterte-supporters-all-set-million-people-march|title=Duterte supporters all set for 'million people march'|publisher=ABS-CBN News|date=2015-09-25|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2016-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160427175010/http://news.abs-cbn.com/nation/09/25/15/duterte-supporters-all-set-million-people-march|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/metro-manila/09/25/15/rally-duterte-not-million-people-march|title=Rally for Duterte not a 'million people march'|publisher=ABS-CBN News|date=2015-09-26|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2015-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927234326/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/metro-manila/09/25/15/rally-duterte-not-million-people-march|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雖然杜特地沒有宣佈參選，但[[亞洲脈搏|亞洲脈搏]]研究總監安娜·塔本達仍然認為杜特地是「一个有力的竞争者」，因為他在該機構在2015年8月至9月所發表的總統民意調查中排名第四，而在[[社會氣象站|社會氣象站]]的民意調查中，杜特地同樣排名第四<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.abs-cbn.com/focus/09/28/15/pulse-asia-poll-duterte-now-serious-contender|title=Pulse Asia poll: Duterte now a serious contender|publisher=ABS-CBN News|date=2015-09-28|accessdate=2016-03-31|archive-date=2016-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311080845/http://news.abs-cbn.com/focus/09/28/15/pulse-asia-poll-duterte-now-serious-contender|dead-url=no}}</ref>。杜特地的政治對手，前[[菲律賓眾議院|眾議院]]議長[[普羅斯佩羅·諾格拉萊斯|普羅斯佩羅·諾格拉萊斯]]亦表示如果杜特地宣佈參選總統，他會支持<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sunstar.com.ph/manila/local-news/2015/09/28/nograles-declares-support-dutertes-presidential-bid-432787|title=Nograles declares support for Duterte's presidential bid|date=2015-09-28|accessdate=2016-04-02|publisher=Sun Star Manila|archive-date=2016-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160326023615/http://www.sunstar.com.ph/manila/local-news/2015/09/28/nograles-declares-support-dutertes-presidential-bid-432787|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年9月29日，參議員艾倫·彼得·卡耶坦奧在達沃市宣佈參選副總統，並表示杜特地是出選總統的第一人選。此促使杜特地與卡耶坦奧會晤<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/09/30/15/cayetano-woos-duterte-we-need-real-leader|title=Cayetano woos Duterte: We need a real leader|date=2015-09-30|accessdate=2016-04-02|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003035107/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/09/30/15/cayetano-woos-duterte-we-need-real-leader|dead-url=no}}</ref>。會晤後一天，杜特地亦在達沃市與另一位打算參選副總統的小费迪南德·马科斯會晤。此時，杜特地仍表示他不會參選總統<ref>{{cite news|url=http://cnnphilippines.com/news/2015/10/01/Rodrigo-Duterte-meets-Bongbong-Marcos-a-day-after-Cayetano.html|title=Marcos meets with Duterte in Davao City|date=2015-10-01|accessdate=2016-04-02|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201627/http://cnnphilippines.com/news/2015/10/01/Rodrigo-Duterte-meets-Bongbong-Marcos-a-day-after-Cayetano.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年10月13日，杜特地在達沃市召開記者會作出最後回應，他表示由於其女兒莎拉的反對，他不會參選總統<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2015/10/13/1510175/duterte-insists-im-not-running|title=Duterte insists: I’m not running|first=Edith|last=Regalado|publisher=The Philippine Star|date=2015-10-13|accessdate=2016-04-03|archive-date=2015-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151223184024/http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2015/10/13/1510175/duterte-insists-im-not-running|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年10月15日，杜特地向達沃市選舉辦事處遞交參選達沃市市長的提名表格<ref>{{cite news|url=http://cnnphilippines.com/news/2015/10/15/rodrigo-duterte-davao-mayor-reelection-elections-2016.html|title=Rodrigo Duterte to seek re-election as Davao City mayor|first=Ben O.|last=Tesiorna|date=2015-10-16|accessdate=2016-04-03|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304123433/http://cnnphilippines.com/news/2015/10/15/rodrigo-duterte-davao-mayor-reelection-elections-2016.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一天後，杜特地的女兒莎拉在[[Instagram|Instagram]]表示，她已宣佈參選達沃市市長一職，引來其父親打算尋求更高級職位並退出達沃市市長選舉的揣測<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/540914/news/regions/sara-duterte-prepares-coc-for-davao-mayor-hints-at-dad-s-presidential-run|title=Sara Duterte prepares COC for Davao mayor, hints at dad's presidential run|publisher=GMA News Online|date=2015-10-16|accessdate=2016-04-03|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304073257/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/540914/news/regions/sara-duterte-prepares-coc-for-davao-mayor-hints-at-dad-s-presidential-run|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但是，達沃市選舉委員會沒有收到莎拉的提名表格<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/540942/news/regions/duterte-aide-sara-didn-t-file-coc-for-mayor|title=Duterte aide: Sara didn’t file COC for mayor|date=2015-10-16|accessdate=2016-04-03|publisher=GMA News Online|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304082704/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/540942/news/regions/duterte-aide-sara-didn-t-file-coc-for-mayor|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年12月10日，與杜特地同屬民主黨的馬丁·迪尼奧在最後一刻提交提名表格<ref>{{cite news|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/731841/duterte-i-wont-be-a-substitute-candidate|title=Duterte: ‘I won’t be a substitute candidate’|publisher=Inquirer.net|date=2015-10-16|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304092440/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/731841/duterte-i-wont-be-a-substitute-candidate|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其後表示自己在將參選[[帕賽市|帕賽市]]市長的提名表格拿作參選總統。在帕賽市舉行的會議上，民主黨決定支持迪尼奧<ref>{{cite web|title = PDP-Laban’s Martin Diño says he’s not a spare tire|url = http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/542017/news/nation/pdp-laban-s-martin-dino-says-he-s-not-a-spare-tire|website = GMA News|accessdate = 2015-10-26|date = 2015-10-26|archive-date = 2015-11-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151122133358/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/542017/news/nation/pdp-laban-s-martin-dino-says-he-s-not-a-spare-tire|dead-url = no}}</ref>。同年10月21日，杜特地接受[[菲律賓有線新聞網絡|菲律賓有線新聞網絡]]訪問時表示，他仍有機會改變主意，但只會在民主黨作出決定時才有這個可能<ref>{{cite news|url=http://cnnphilippines.com/news/2015/10/22/Duterte-Its-up-to-PDP-Laban-to-substitute-me-for-Di%C3%B1o-as-standard-bearer.html|title=Duterte: It's up to PDP-Laban to substitute me as standard bearer|publisher=CNN Philippines|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115908/http://cnnphilippines.com/news/2015/10/22/Duterte-Its-up-to-PDP-Laban-to-substitute-me-for-Di%C3%B1o-as-standard-bearer.html|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2015年10月27日，民主黨宣佈如果迪尼奧退選或被選舉委員會取消資格，就會由杜特地替補<ref>{{cite news|url=http://cnnphilippines.com/news/2015/10/27/Rodrigo-Rody-Duterte-Martin-Dino-2016-elections-PDP-Laban-president.html|title=PDP-Laban decision final: Duterte to substitute if Diño withdraws presidential bid|publisher=CNN Philippines|date=2015-10-28|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304124142/http://cnnphilippines.com/news/2015/10/27/Rodrigo-Rody-Duterte-Martin-Dino-2016-elections-PDP-Laban-president.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩天後，迪尼奧表示由於自己的參選可能無效，宣佈退選，並宣佈由杜特地替補<ref>{{cite web|last1=Takumi|first1=Rie|title=Martin Diño withdraws candidacy for president, names Duterte as substitute|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/542407/news/nation/martin-dino-withdraws-candidacy-for-president-names-duterte-as-substitute|website=gmanetwork.com|accessdate=2015-10-29|archive-date=2015-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031220325/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/542407/news/nation/martin-dino-withdraws-candidacy-for-president-names-duterte-as-substitute|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年10月21日，杜特地在母校[[聖貝達學院|聖貝達學院]]正式宣佈參選總統，並接受艾倫·彼得·卡耶坦奧的邀請，成為其競選搭檔<ref>{{cite web|title=Duterte makes a stand|url=http://www.mb.com.ph/duterte-makes-a-stand/#LubMmVQSGTGM834v.99|website=Manila Bulletin|accessdate=2015-11-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123202534/http://www.mb.com.ph/duterte-makes-a-stand/#LubMmVQSGTGM834v.99|archivedate=2015-11-23}}</ref>。杜特地表示，他對参议院选举法庭對格蕾丝·波因的公民權的裁決和當時政府處理[[2015年尼諾伊·阿基諾國際機場種票事件|尼諾伊·阿基諾國際機場種票事件]]的表現表示失望<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.kickerdaily.com/duterte-open-to-running-disappointed-over-poe-decision-and-laglag-bala/|title=Duterte now open to running, says he is disappointed over Poe decision and ‘laglag-bala’|work=Kicker Daily News|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122083736/http://m.kickerdaily.com/duterte-open-to-running-disappointed-over-poe-decision-and-laglag-bala/|archivedate=2015-11-22|accessdate=2016-04-15}}</ref>。杜特地表示向民主黨表達意向後會即時遞交提名表格<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/regions/11/21/15/duterte-decides-to-run-for-president|title=Duterte decides to run for president|publisher=ABS-CBN News|date=2015-11-22|accessdate=2016-04-05|archive-date=2015-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212011029/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/regions/11/21/15/duterte-decides-to-run-for-president|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但是，杜特地取代迪尼奧的合法性受到一些選舉律師的質疑，因為迪尼奧的提名表格表示他會競逐帕賽市市長的職務，但迪尼奧自己是[[奎松市|奎松市]]的居民。

杜特地在由亞洲脈搏在2015年11月25日進行的民意調查中居首<ref>{{cite web|title=Duterte leads in Metro poll|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/742540/duterte-leads-in-metro-poll|website=inquirer.net|accessdate=2015-11-26|archive-date=2015-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126135145/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/742540/duterte-leads-in-metro-poll|dead-url=no}}</ref>。格蕾丝·波因表示該民調存在不確定性和不能反映真實情況，並表示該民意調查是由杜特地陣營發動的<ref>{{cite web|title=Poe camp calls poll topped by Duterte ‘inconclusive’|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/742649/poe-camp-calls-poll-topped-by-duterte-inconclusive|website=Inquirer|accessdate=2015-11-26|archive-date=2015-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126233926/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/742649/poe-camp-calls-poll-topped-by-duterte-inconclusive|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一天後，杜特地在馬尼拉的選舉委員會辦事處撤回達沃市市長的提名表格，而其提名改由其女兒莎拉·杜特地替補<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/545982/news/nation/duterte-files-coc-for-president|title=Duterte files COC for president|publisher=GMA News|date=2015-11-27|accessdate=2015-11-27|archive-date=2015-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151130021115/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/545982/news/nation/duterte-files-coc-for-president|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====格蕾丝·波因====
格蕾丝·波因在2013年參議院選舉中以有史以來無黨籍候選人所得的最高票數當選，此讓其成為2016年總統選舉的潛在竞争者，但她在2014年4月否認會出選總統，表示她不考慮「參選參議員以上的職位」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/590668/grace-poe-says-shes-not-ready-for-2016-palace-run|title=Grace Poe says she’s not ready for 2016 Palace run|first=TJ|last=Burgonio|work=Philippine Daily Inquirer|date=2014-04-01|accessdate=2016-04-15|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081714/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/590668/grace-poe-says-shes-not-ready-for-2016-palace-run|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年5月，阿基諾總統出訪加拿大。出發前，阿基諾表示曾與波因會面，但沒有透露詳情<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/484522/news/nation/pnoy-confirms-talking-politics-with-poe-but-is-mum-on-details |title=PNoy confirms talking politics with Poe but is mum on details |first=Andrei |last=Medina |work=GMA News Online |date=2015-05-09 |accessdate=2015-05-17 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518095608/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/484522/news/nation/pnoy-confirms-talking-politics-with-poe-but-is-mum-on-details |dead-url=no }}</ref>。幾天後，波因表示她有與阿基諾會面，並表示他們在討論阿基諾對總統候選人的看法。她表示阿基諾想選出一個國家信任和有潛在勝算的候選人，以维持政府的反貪改革及扶貧措施。她也表示期待在6月與阿基諾有更多會面機會<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.interaksyon.com/article/110344/poe-pnoy-offered-no-position-yet-more-talks-seen-this-june |title=Poe: PNoy offered no position yet, more talks seen this June |first=Ernie |last=Reyes |work=Interaksyon.com |date=2015-05-11 |accessdate=2015-05-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518095936/http://www.interaksyon.com/article/110344/poe-pnoy-offered-no-position-yet-more-talks-seen-this-june |archivedate=2015-05-18 }}</ref>。

2015年6月2日，聯合民族主義聯盟代總裁[[托比·蒂昂科|托比·蒂昂科]]在記者會上被質問有關民眾要求比奈全盤托出其貪污指控的問題時，表示波因不合資格參選總統或副總統，因為在2013年參議院選舉中，她只在菲律賓居住了六年零六個月，再加上2016年總統選舉的3年，亦只有9年零6個月，比憲法規定的居住年限短半年<ref>{{Cite web|title = Grace Poe lacks residency, not qualified to run for president or VP – solon|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/695676/grace-poe-lacks-residency-not-qualified-to-run-as-president-or-vp-solon|website = INQUIRER,net|accessdate = June 7, 2015|first = Marc|last = Cayabyab|date = 2015-06-02|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304092233/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/695676/grace-poe-lacks-residency-not-qualified-to-run-as-president-or-vp-solon|dead-url = no}}</ref>。兩天後，波因在參議院會議前表示，自己在提名表格上寫自己在菲律賓只居住了六年零六個月，是因為她在2006年4月才將自己在美國的家售出。波因曾在美國居住了13年，直至其父親[[費爾南多·波因|費爾南多·波因]]在2004年12月逝世為止。她表示自己自2005年2月開始便住在菲律賓。她亦表示，除了當國會議員外，她有百分之五十肯定自己會參選2016年的總統選舉。她也表示聯合民族主義聯盟只是在她簽署參議院藍絲帶委員會調查比奈的報告之後才開始抨擊她<ref>{{Cite web|title = Grace Poe: I’m qualified|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/696058/grace-poe-im-qualified|website = Philippine Daily Inquirer|accessdate = 2015-06-07|first = |last = |date = 2015-06-04|archive-date = 2015-06-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150619211921/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/696058/grace-poe-im-qualified|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2015年9月16日，波因在[[菲律賓大學迪里曼分校|菲律賓大學迪里曼分校]]宣佈參選總統，她亦表示沒有人或政黨可以壟斷阿基諾總統的繼續推行直線政策的路線，此番說話將矛頭指向自由黨候選人，提倡繼續推行阿基諾直線政策的羅哈斯。波因在演說中亦抨擊政府推行的政策，此導致[[馬拉坎南宮|馬拉坎南宮]]質疑他們的演說中有哪些與直線政策不符的地方<ref>{{Cite web|title = Poe in 2016|url = http://www.mb.com.ph/poe-in-2016/|website = Manila Bulletin|accessdate = 2015-09-17|first = Hannah|last = Torregoza|date = 2015-09-16|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150920000423/http://www.mb.com.ph/poe-in-2016/|archivedate = 2015-09-20}}</ref>。

2015年12月1日，選舉委員會以其不符合公民權和居住年期限制為理由，正式駁回波因的提名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/546387/news/nation/comelec-division-disqualifies-poe-from-2016-presidential-race|title=Comelec division disqualifies Poe from 2016 presidential race|publisher=GMA News Online|date=2015-12-01|accessdate=2015-12-01|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208165645/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/546387/news/nation/comelec-division-disqualifies-poe-from-2016-presidential-race|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年12月23日，選舉委員會全體委員裁定波因無法達到居住菲律賓10年的要求<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rappler.com/nation/politics/elections/2016/116912-comelec-en-banc-bars-grace-poe-from-running|title=Comelec en banc bars Grace Poe from running in 2016|publisher=Rappler.com|date=2015-12-23|accessdate=2015-12-23|archive-date=2015-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151226014736/http://www.rappler.com/nation/politics/elections/2016/116912-comelec-en-banc-bars-grace-poe-from-running|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>}{{cite news|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/philippines-election-faces-turmoil-as-favorite-grace-poe-disqualified-1450864915|title=Philippines Election Faces Turmoil as Favorite Grace Poe Disqualified|publisher=The Wall Street Journal|date=2015-12-23|accessdate=2016-04-15|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422160313/http://www.wsj.com/articles/philippines-election-faces-turmoil-as-favorite-grace-poe-disqualified-1450864915|dead-url=no}}</ref>。波因表示會向最高法院上訴。2015年12月28日，最高法院發出兩張[[临时禁制令|临时禁制令]]，暫緩選舉委員會的決定<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/philippines-presidential-election-grace-poe-kept-ballot-now-supreme-court-2241801|title=Philippines Presidential Election: Grace Poe Kept On Ballot For Now By Supreme Court|publisher=International Business Times|date=2015-12-28|accessdate=2016-04-15|archive-date=2016-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160128233634/http://www.ibtimes.com/philippines-presidential-election-grace-poe-kept-ballot-now-supreme-court-2241801|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====馬爾·羅哈斯====
參議院議長[[富蘭克林·德里隆|富蘭克林·德里隆]]在2013年1月向傳媒表示，馬爾·羅哈斯是自由黨參選2016年總統選舉最適合的人選<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/292590/news/nation/drilon-mar-roxas-is-lp-s-bet-in-2016-presidential-polls |title=Drilon: Mar Roxas is LP's bet in 2016 presidential polls |work=GMA News Online |date=2013-01-13 |accessdate=2016-04-15 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093013/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/292590/news/nation/drilon-mar-roxas-is-lp-s-bet-in-2016-presidential-polls |dead-url=no }}</ref>。兩年後，德里隆表示羅哈斯已在自由黨內部表達參選總統的意願<ref>{{cite news |url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/686291/surprise-roxas-tells-lp-he-will-run-in-2016 |title=Surprise: Roxas tells LP he will run in 2016 |work=Philippine Daily Inquirer |first1=Leila B. |last1=Salaverria |first2=Niña P. |last2=Calleja |date=2015-04-18 |accessdate=2015-04-18 |archive-date=2015-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150419194249/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/686291/surprise-roxas-tells-lp-he-will-run-in-2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。部份自由黨中堅份子希望羅哈斯在此時宣佈參選<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/489246/news/nation/drilon-tells-mar-roxas-declare-plan-to-run-for-president|title = Drilon tells Mar Roxas: Declare plan to run for President|last = Legaspi|first = Amita O.|date = 2015-05-18|work = GMA News Online|access-date = 2015-05-20|via = |archive-date = 2015-05-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150521120108/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/489246/news/nation/drilon-tells-mar-roxas-declare-plan-to-run-for-president|dead-url = no}}</ref>，但[[菲律賓預算及管理部|預算及管理部]]部長[[弗洛倫西奧·阿巴德|弗洛倫西奧·阿巴德]]建議羅哈斯改選副總統<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/691932/roxas-may-slide-down-for-poe-says-lp|title = Roxas may slide down for Poe, says LP|last = Esguerra|first = Christian V.|date = 2015-05-17|work = INQUIRER.net|access-date = May 20, 2015|via = |archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304095233/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/691932/roxas-may-slide-down-for-poe-says-lp|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2015年5月，阿基諾訪問加拿大前與羅哈斯、格蕾丝·波因和弗朗西斯·埃斯庫德羅會面。其後阿基諾在7月發表其任內最後一份國情咨文前，與羅哈斯等三人在馬拉坎南宮共進晚餐。羅哈斯被視為阿基諾的接班人，誰成為羅哈斯的競選搭檔便成為焦點。格蕾丝·波因表示她選擇埃斯庫德羅作為其競選搭檔<ref>{{Cite web|title = Aquino hosts make-or-break dinner meeting|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/705436/dinner-meeting-among-aquino-poe-roxas-escudero-ongoing|website = INQUIRER.net|accessdate = 2015-08-01|first = |last = |date = 2015-07-16|archive-date = 2015-07-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150721093743/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/705436/dinner-meeting-among-aquino-poe-roxas-escudero-ongoing|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2015年7月31日，羅哈斯宣佈接受自由黨的提名，出選2016年總統選舉，並獲總統阿基諾三世的支持<ref name=":4">{{cite news|url = http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/531033/news/nation/emotional-roxas-accepts-pnoy-endorsement|title = Emotional Roxas accepts PNoy endorsement|work = GMA News|date = 2015-07-31|accessdate = 2015-07-31|archive-date = 2015-09-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924145207/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/531033/news/nation/emotional-roxas-accepts-pnoy-endorsement|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

