====艾倫·彼得·卡耶坦奧====
2013年3月，國民黨參議員艾倫·彼得·卡耶坦奧接受[[ABS-CBN|ABS-CBN]]訪問時表示想成為總統<ref>{{cite news|url = https://anc.yahoo.com/news/senator-alan-cayetano-on-2016-polls--i-don%E2%80%99t-want-to-run--i-want-to-win-060709390.html|title = Senator Alan Cayetano on 2016 polls: ‘I want to be president’|work = ANC - Yahoo|date = 2014-04-05|accessdate = 2014-06-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140308155238/http://anc.yahoo.com/news/senator-alan-cayetano-on-2016-polls--i-don%E2%80%99t-want-to-run--i-want-to-win-060709390.html|archive-date = 2014-03-08|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

卡耶坦奧在達沃市與羅德里戈·杜特地會面後，表示他會競逐副總統一職。作為國民黨一員，卡耶坦奧表示國民黨將召開會議決定其競選搭檔<ref>{{Cite web|title = Cayetano to run for VP|url = http://www.philstar.com/election-2016/latest-news/2015/09/29/1505238/cayetano-run-vp|first = Patricia Lourdes|last = Viray|accessdate = 2015-09-29|website = INQUIRER.net|date = 2015-09-19|archive-date = 2015-10-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151001120757/http://www.philstar.com/election-2016/latest-news/2015/09/29/1505238/cayetano-run-vp|dead-url = no}}</ref>。10月1日，杜特地表示如果他競逐總統職務，他會選擇卡耶坦奧作為競選搭檔<ref>{{Cite web|title = Duterte wants Cayetano as 2016 running mate if he decides to run|url = http://www.businessmirror.com.ph/duterte-wants-cayetano-as-2016-running-mate-if-he-decides-to-run/|website = The|accessdate = 2015-10-15|publisher = |last = |first = |date = 2015-10-01|archive-date = 2015-10-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151005053041/http://www.businessmirror.com.ph/duterte-wants-cayetano-as-2016-running-mate-if-he-decides-to-run/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。幾天後，杜特地拒絕卡耶坦奧和小费迪南德·马科斯的競選搭檔邀請<ref>{{Cite web|title = Duterte declines team-up offer of Cayetano, Marcos|url = http://www.mindanews.com/top-stories/2015/10/04/duterte-declines-team-up-offer-of-cayetano-marcos/|website = MindaNews|accessdate = 2015-10-15|last = Colina|date = 2015-10-04|first = Antonio L. IV|archive-date = 2015-10-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151009033126/http://www.mindanews.com/top-stories/2015/10/04/duterte-declines-team-up-offer-of-cayetano-marcos/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。但是，在2015年11月，卡耶坦奧確認如果杜特地參選總統，他便會是杜特地的競選搭檔<ref>{{cite news|last1=Calleja|first1=Niña|last2=Ubac|first2=Michael Lim|title=IT’S OFFICIAL: Duterte, Cayetano team up for 2016|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/741458/its-official-duterte-cayetano-team-up-for-2016|accessdate=2015-11-24|work=Philippine Daily Inquirer|date=2015-11-22|archive-date=2015-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124045157/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/741458/its-official-duterte-cayetano-team-up-for-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====弗朗西斯·埃斯庫德羅====
無黨籍參議員弗朗西斯·埃斯庫德羅2012年3月接受訪問時表示，有興趣在2016年競逐更高職位的選舉<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rappler.com/nation/4118--very-interested-in-2016-race|title=Chiz 'very interested' in 2016 race|first=Carmela|last=Fonbuena|work=Rappler.com|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2016-04-15|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912104357/https://www.rappler.com/nation/4118-chiz-very-interested-in-2016-race|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年5月，格蕾丝·波因向記者表示如果埃斯庫德羅參選總統，她便不會參選<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rappler.com/nation/93123-francis-escudero-2016-plans |title=Escudero on 2016: Poe and I haven't decided |first=Ayee |last=Macaraig |work=Rappler.com |date=2014-05-14 |accessdate=2015-05-24 |archive-date=2015-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150726021257/http://www.rappler.com/nation/93123-francis-escudero-2016-plans |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年9月17日，埃斯庫德羅在[[仙範市|仙範市]]宣佈參選副總統，並成為波因的競選搭檔<ref name=":5"/>。

====格雷戈里奧·霍納桑====
聯合民族主義聯盟參議員格雷戈里奧·霍納桑在2015年9月曾否認自己會成為傑約馬爾·比奈的競選搭檔<ref>{{Cite web|title = Honasan denies tandem with Binay in 2016 polls|url = http://www.sunstar.com.ph/manila/local-news/2015/09/22/honasan-denies-tandem-binay-2016-polls-431698|website = Sun.Star Manila|accessdate = 2015-10-15|date = 2015-09-22|last = Gita|first = Ruth Abbey|archive-date = 2015-09-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150928081946/http://www.sunstar.com.ph/manila/local-news/2015/09/22/honasan-denies-tandem-binay-2016-polls-431698|dead-url = no}}</ref>。但在同年10月，他又表示可能會成為比奈的競選搭檔<ref>{{Cite web|title = ‘Bi-Hon’ tandem in 2016 possible, says Honasan|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/728038/bi-hon-tandem-in-2016-possible-says-honasan|website = INQUIRER.net|accessdate = 2015-10-15|date = 2015-10-05|last = Ager|first = Maila|archive-date = 2015-10-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151008094905/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/728038/bi-hon-tandem-in-2016-possible-says-honasan|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2015年10月12日，霍納桑宣佈參選副總統，並成為比奈的競選搭檔<ref name=":8"/>。

====小费迪南德·马科斯====
2012年11月，國民黨參議員小费迪南德·马科斯接受訪問時被問及是否在2016年參選總統時表示「永不說不」<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.rappler.com/nation/politics/elections-2013/16735-marcos-on-2016-never-say-never|title = Marcos on 2016: Never say never|first = Ayee|last = Macaraig|work = Rappler.com|date = 2012-11-25|accessdate = 2016-04-15|archive-date = 2018-11-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181106195806/https://www.rappler.com/nation/politics/elections-2013/16735-marcos-on-2016-never-say-never|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2015年3月，馬可斯接受另一個訪問時表示他會研究參選的可行性<ref>{{cite news|url = http://manilastandardtoday.com/2015/03/23/bongbong-admits-he-s-eyeing-presidential-run/|title = Bongbong admits he’s eyeing presidential run|first = Macon|last = Ramos-Araneta|work = Manila Standard Today|date = 2015-03-23|accessdate = 2015-03-24|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150330011959/http://manilastandardtoday.com/2015/03/23/bongbong-admits-he-s-eyeing-presidential-run|archivedate = 2015-03-30}}</ref>。2015年8月，有報道指出他會成為傑約馬爾·比奈的競選搭檔，馬可斯接受ABS-CBN訪問時表示他仍未決定參選哪一職位，但他肯定不會在參議院尋求連任<ref>{{Cite web|title = Bongbong Marcos mulls over Palace run|url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/716677/bongbong-marcos-mulls-over-palace-run|website = Philippine Daily Inquirer|accessdate = 2015-08-27|first = Leila B.|last = Salaverria|date = 2015-08-27|archive-date = 2015-08-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150828001211/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/716677/bongbong-marcos-mulls-over-palace-run|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2015年10月5日，小费迪南德·马科斯宣佈參選副總統，並表示如果羅德里戈·杜特地參選，就會支持他<ref name=":7"/>。

====萊妮·羅布雷多====
2015年8月，自由黨眾議員萊妮·羅布雷多表示她只會在「必須」的情況下才會在2016年參選副總統，並表示在2016年參選副總統是過早<ref>{{Cite web|title = Leni Robredo on VP race: 'Too soon'|url = http://www.rappler.com/nation/politics/elections/2016/101538-leni-robredo-vp-race-too-soon|website = Rappler|accessdate = 2015-08-05|last = Cupin|first = Bea|date = 2015-08-04|archive-date = 2015-08-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150807092442/http://www.rappler.com/nation/politics/elections/2016/101538-leni-robredo-vp-race-too-soon|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

雖然女兒反對，羅布雷多仍決定參選副總統，並接受阿基諾總統和馬爾·羅哈斯的邀請，成為羅哈斯的競選搭檔<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lozada|first1=Aaron|title=What convinced Leni Robredo to run for VP|url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/focus/10/05/15/what-convinced-leni-robredo-run-vp|accessdate=October 6, 2015|work=ABS-CBN News and Current Affairs|publisher=ABS-CBN Corporation|date=2015-10-05|archive-date=2015-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151213202938/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/focus/10/05/15/what-convinced-leni-robredo-run-vp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她在2015年10月5日宣佈參選副總統<ref name=":6"/>。

====安东尼奥·特里兰尼斯====
2014年5月30日，國民黨參議員[[安东尼奥·特里兰尼斯|安东尼奥·特里兰尼斯]]接受訪問時表示在2016年會參選副總統，但最後參選哪個職位仍尊重國民黨的決定<ref>{{cite news|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/606869/trillanes-i-will-run-for-a-higher-position-in-2016|title=Trillanes: I will run for a higher position in 2016|first=Maila|last=Ager|work=Philippine Daily Inquirer|date=2014-05-30|accessdate=2016-04-15|archive-date=2016-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527045734/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/606869/trillanes-i-will-run-for-a-higher-position-in-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年8月，特里利安埃斯表示他會以無黨籍身份參選副總統，並表示由於國民黨有多於一個人參選副總統，國民黨不會支持任何一位候選人。特里兰尼斯所屬的另一政黨[[馬格達洛黨|馬格達洛黨]]支持其參選<ref>{{Cite web|title = Trillanes to run as independent VP in 2016|url = http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2015/08/19/1489828/trillanes-run-independent-vp-2016|accessdate = 2015-09-20|date = 2015-08-19|publisher = The Philippine Star|last = Viray|first = Patricia Lourdes|archive-date = 2015-09-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150921182456/http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2015/08/19/1489828/trillanes-run-independent-vp-2016|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

在一次馬格達洛黨大會上，特里兰尼斯宣佈以無黨籍身份參選副總統，並支持格蕾丝·波因參選總統<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.interaksyon.com/article/118440/as-poe-thanks-trillanes-binay-camp-blasts-senators-vp-bid|title=As Poe thanks Trillanes, Binay camp blasts senator's VP bid|work=InterAksyon.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208090433/http://www.interaksyon.com/article/118440/as-poe-thanks-trillanes-binay-camp-blasts-senators-vp-bid|archivedate=2015-12-08|accessdate=2016-04-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2015/10/04/1507046/chiz-grateful-trillanes-magdalos-poe-endorsement|title=Chiz grateful for Trillanes, Magdalo’s Poe endorsement|work=philstar.com|accessdate=2016-04-15|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208080807/http://www.philstar.com/headlines/2015/10/04/1507046/chiz-grateful-trillanes-magdalos-poe-endorsement|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

